OL,3,CUp to 150 former WH Smith stores to
OL,4,Cclose
OL,6,FThe closure of up to 150 high street
OL,7,Fstores, previously part of the WH
OL,8,FSmith business, is the "direct result
OL,9,Fof government policy and recent
OL,10,Fgeopolitical events", its owners have
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FIt is understood hundreds of jobs at
OL,14,FTGJones are at risk as part of the
OL,15,Frestructuring plans the company said
OL,16,Fwere necessary after the last 12
OL,17,Fmonths of "highly challenging trading
OL,18,Fconditions".
