OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778148400
OL,3,CUp to 150 former WH Smith stores to
OL,4,Cclose
OL,6,FThe shops were rebranded under the
OL,7,Fname TGJones after the purchase of 480
OL,8,FWH Smith stores by Modella Capital
OL,9,Flast year.
OL,11,FIn a statement provided to the Press
OL,12,FAssociation on Wednesday, a
OL,13,Fspokesperson for the business said the
OL,14,Fdecision to restructure the company
OL,15,F"had not been taken lightly".
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@\O]
