FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778148400
OL,3,CUp to 150 former WH Smith stores to
OL,4,Cclose
OL,6,FThe statement said: "While we continue
OL,7,Fto believe in the strength of the core
OL,8,Fbusiness, TGJones has experienced
OL,9,Fhighly challenging trading conditions
OL,10,Fover the past year, along with many
OL,11,Fother brick-and-mortar retailers.
