FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778148400
OL,3,CUp to 150 former WH Smith stores to
OL,4,Cclose
OL,6,F"Weak consumer spending and cost-of-
OL,7,Fliving pressures, combined with rising
OL,8,Foperating costs as a direct result of
OL,9,Fgovernment policy and recent
OL,10,Fgeopolitical events, have meant that
OL,11,Fthe company as a whole has remained
OL,12,Floss-making.
OL,14,F"The forced name change from WH Smith
OL,15,Fhas also negatively impacted consumer
OL,16,Fawareness, despite the fact that the
OL,17,Fproposition has improved."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
