FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778148400
OL,3,CUp to 150 former WH Smith stores to
OL,4,Cclose
OL,6,FThe statement continued: "The survival
OL,7,Fof this iconic 234-year-old business
OL,8,Fis our imperative. No decisions have
OL,9,Fyet been taken on how this will impact
OL,10,Froles, but we will aim to preserve as
OL,11,Fmany jobs as possible.
OL,13,F"Any potential store closures or role
OL,14,Freductions will be subject to
OL,15,Fappropriate consultation, and we are
OL,16,Fcommitted to engaging openly and
OL,17,Fconstructively with colleagues and
OL,18,Ftheir representatives.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
