OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778148400
OL,3,CUp to 150 former WH Smith stores to
OL,4,Cclose
OL,6,F"We want to be clear, however, that
OL,7,Fthe plan may result in the closure of
OL,8,Fsome stores and the loss of some roles.
OL,10,F"We recognise the impact this
OL,11,Funcertainty will have on colleagues,
OL,12,Ftheir families and the communities we
OL,13,Fserve."
